name: Resting Ondel
description:
Ondel-Ondel; carried on Public Transportation.

It's sadden me the most to witness a once Jakarta's iconic puppet figure, that regularly perfomed at traditional festive, has shift it's path to street side, for the sake of surviving.

The beauty of life, is naturally change.

Shot on Canon EOS 5/Kodak Colorplus 200 | C41 Process | Noritsu Scan | 3130 × 2075px
